Interface TypeRegistry

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    MetaStore, MutableMetaStore
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MetaStoreImpl, TypeRegistryImpl

    public interface TypeRegistry
    TypeRegistry maintains a mapping from custom schema names to more complicated schemas.
